cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the evaluation of Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL) algorithms on Atari games, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper proposes a standardized benchmark for evaluating DRL algorithms on Atari games, which is relevant to all of these sub-categories.
